data.description: Here comes the opportunity you have been waiting for to own a home at the College Neighborhood! This stunning home features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, open concept kitchen with granite counter tops, breakfast area 2 living rooms, plenty of cabinets for lots of storage! New AC unit, newer windows and handicap accessible. The backyard is nice and cozy perfect for the family gatherings and Holidays.  This gem is located close to schools, shopping centers, highways and nice restaurants! You don't want to miss out on this opportunity  schedule your private showing TODAY!
